query:
INSERT INTO exercises (
            id,
            course_id,
            name,
            deadline,
            page_id,
            score_maximum,
            order_number,
            chapter_id,
            copied_from,
            exercise_language_group_id
          )
        SELECT uuid_generate_v5($1, id::text),
          $1,
          name,
          deadline,
          uuid_generate_v5($1, page_id::text),
          score_maximum,
          order_number,
          uuid_generate_v5($1, chapter_id::text),
          id,
          exercise_language_group_id
        FROM exercises
        WHERE course_id = $2
        AND deleted_at IS NULL
        RETURNING id,
          copied_from;
